dynamicLookup.nsql: SELECT @SELECT:CM.ID:CONNECTION_ID@, @SELECT:CM.CODE:CONNECTION_CODE@, @SELECT:CM.NAME:CONNECTION_NAME@, @SELECT:CM.REGO_CONN_TYPE:CONNECTION_TYPE_ID@, @SELECT:CT.NAME:CONNECTION_TYPE@ FROM ODF_CA_REGO_CONN_MANAGER CM JOIN CMN_LOOKUPS_V CT ON CM.REGO_CONN_TYPE = CT.LOOKUP_ENUM AND CT.LOOKUP_TYPE = 'REGO_CONN_TYPE' AND CT.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_ACTION_ID@ IS NULL) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ODF_CA_REGO_DATA_ACTION DA WHERE @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_ACTION_ID@ = DA.ID AND ( (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE IN (7, 9) AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM IN (1, 2)) OR /* XOG */ (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE IN (4, 10, 24) AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM IN (3, 5, 8, 9, 12)) OR /* HTTP */ (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE = 16 AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM = 9) /* LOCAL REST */ OR (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE = 8 AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM = 4) OR /* PORTAL */ (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE = 22 AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM IN (10, 11)) /* SFTP */ ) ) ) @BROWSE-ONLY: AND CM.REGO_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND CT.IS_ACTIVE = 1 :BROWSE-ONLY@ AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:CA.ID:ATTRIBUTE_ID@ , @SELECT:CA.COLUMN_NAME:ATTRIBUTE_CODE@ , @SELECT:CAN.NAME:ATTRIBUTE_NAME@ FROM ODF_OBJECTS O JOIN ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES CA ON O.CODE = CA.OBJECT_NAME JOIN CMN_CAPTIONS_NLS CAN ON CA.ID = CAN.PK_ID AND CAN.TABLE_NAME = 'ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES' AND CAN.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ = O.CODE) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ IS NULL) ) AND CA.DATA_TYPE = 'clob' AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:O.ID:OBJECT_ID@ , @SELECT:O.CODE:OBJECT_CODE@ , @SELECT:ONN.NAME:OBJECT_NAME@ FROM ODF_OBJECTS O JOIN CMN_CAPTIONS_NLS ONN ON O.ID = ONN.PK_ID AND ONN.TABLE_NAME = 'ODF_OBJECTS' AND ONN.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE O.IS_CUSTOM = 1 AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:DP.ID:ID@ , @SELECT:DP.CODE:CODE@ , @SELECT:DP.NAME:NAME@ , @SELECT:DP.REGO_SORT_ORDER:SORT_ORDER@
FROM ODF_CA_REGO_DATA_PROCESSOR DP
WHERE 1=1 AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:CM.ID:CONNECTION_ID@ , @SELECT:CM.CODE:CONNECTION_CODE@ , @SELECT:CM.NAME:CONNECTION_NAME@
FROM ODF_CA_REGO_CONN_MANAGER CM JOIN CMN_LOOKUPS_V CT ON CM.REGO_CONN_TYPE = CT.LOOKUP_ENUM AND CT.LOOKUP_TYPE = 'REGO_CONN_TYPE' AND CT.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en'
WHERE CM.REGO_CONN_TYPE IN (6, 7, 14) AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_ACTION_ID@ IS NULL) OR (EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ODF_CA_REGO_DATA_ACTION DA WHERE @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_ACTION_ID@ = DA.ID AND ( (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE IN (3, 11) AND @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:FILE_ENCRYPTION@ = 1 AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM = 6) OR -- DATA IMPORT WITH PGP PRIVATE KEY (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE IN (3, 11) AND @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:FILE_ENCRYPTION@ = 2 AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM = 14) OR -- DATA IMPORT WITH AES KEY (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE = 14 AND @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:FILE_ENCRYPTION@ = 1 AND CT.LOOKUP_ENUM = 7) OR -- DATA EXPORT WITH PUBLIC KEY (DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE = 23 AND @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:FILE_ENCRYPTION@ = 1) -- FILE ENCRYPTION ))) ) @BROWSE-ONLY: AND CM.REGO_IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND CT.IS_ACTIVE = 1 :BROWSE-ONLY@

SELECT @SELECT:DA.ID:ID@ , @SELECT:DA.CODE:CODE@ , @SELECT:DA.NAME:NAME@ , @SELECT:DA.REGO_SORT_ORDER:SORT_ORDER@ FROM ODF_CA_REGO_DATA_ACTION DA WHERE 1=1 AND @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_PROCESS_ID@ = DA.ODF_PARENT_ID AND @WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:CODE@ != DA.CODE AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:SORT_ORDER@ < DA.REGO_SORT_ORDER) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:SORT_ORDER@ IS NULL) ) @BROWSE-ONLY:AND DA.REGO_IS_ACTIVE = 1:BROWSE-ONLY@ AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:FLD.ID:FOLDER_ID@ , @SELECT:FLD.NAME:FOLDER_NAME@ , @SELECT:FLD.PATH_NAME:FOLDER_PATH@ FROM CLB_DMS_FOLDERS KSFLD JOIN CLB_DMS_FLAT_HIERARCHY FH ON KSFLD.ID = FH.ANCESTOR_ID JOIN CLB_DMS_FOLDERS FLD ON FH.CHILD_ID = FLD.ID WHERE KSFLD.NAME = 'KS' AND KSFLD.PATH_NAME = '/Root/DMS' AND KSFLD.FOLDER_TYPE = 'StandardFolder' AND KSFLD.ASSOC_OBJ_TYPE = 'KS' AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:DA.ID:ID@ , @SELECT:DA.CODE:CODE@ , @SELECT:DA.NAME:NAME@ , @SELECT:DA.REGO_SORT_ORDER:SORT_ORDER@ FROM ODF_CA_REGO_DATA_ACTION DA WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:CODE@ != DA.CODE) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:CODE@ IS NULL) ) AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_PROCESS_ID@ = DA.ODF_PARENT_ID) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_PROCESS_ID@ IS NULL) ) @BROWSE-ONLY:AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_ACTION_TYPE@ != 6) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:INTEGER:DATA_ACTION_TYPE@ IS NULL) ):BROWSE-ONLY@ @BROWSE-ONLY:AND DA.REGO_IS_ACTIVE = 1:BROWSE-ONLY@ @BROWSE-ONLY:AND DA.REGO_ACTION_TYPE = 6:BROWSE-ONLY@ AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:CA.ID:ATTRIBUTE_ID@ , @SELECT:CA.COLUMN_NAME:ATTRIBUTE_CODE@ , @SELECT:CAN.NAME:ATTRIBUTE_NAME@ FROM ODF_OBJECTS O JOIN ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES CA ON O.CODE = CA.OBJECT_NAME JOIN CMN_CAPTIONS_NLS CAN ON CA.ID = CAN.PK_ID AND CAN.TABLE_NAME = 'ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES' AND CAN.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ = O.CODE) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ IS NULL) ) AND CA.DATA_TYPE = 'number' AND CA.EXTENDED_TYPE IS NULL AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:CA.ID:ATTRIBUTE_ID@ , @SELECT:CA.COLUMN_NAME:ATTRIBUTE_CODE@ , @SELECT:CAN.NAME:ATTRIBUTE_NAME@ FROM ODF_OBJECTS O JOIN ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES CA ON O.CODE = CA.OBJECT_NAME JOIN CMN_CAPTIONS_NLS CAN ON CA.ID = CAN.PK_ID AND CAN.TABLE_NAME = 'ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES' AND CAN.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ = O.CODE) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ IS NULL) ) AND CA.DATA_TYPE = 'string' AND CA.EXTENDED_TYPE IS NULL AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:CA.ID:ATTRIBUTE_ID@ , @SELECT:CA.COLUMN_NAME:ATTRIBUTE_CODE@ , @SELECT:CAN.NAME:ATTRIBUTE_NAME@ FROM ODF_OBJECTS O JOIN ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES CA ON O.CODE = CA.OBJECT_NAME JOIN CMN_CAPTIONS_NLS CAN ON CA.ID = CAN.PK_ID AND CAN.TABLE_NAME = 'ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES' AND CAN.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ = O.CODE) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ IS NULL) ) AND CA.DATA_TYPE = 'number' AND CA.EXTENDED_TYPE = 'lookup' AND CA.LOOKUP_TYPE = 'REGO_RECORD_STATUS' AND @FILTER@

SELECT @SELECT:A.ATTRIBUTE_ID:ATTRIBUTE_ID@ , @SELECT:A.ATTRIBUTE_CODE:ATTRIBUTE_CODE@ , @SELECT:A.ATTRIBUTE_NAME:ATTRIBUTE_NAME@ , @SELECT:A.DATA_TYPE:DATA_TYPE@ FROM (SELECT -1 ATTRIBUTE_ID , 'id' ATTRIBUTE_CODE , 'ID' ATTRIBUTE_NAME , 'Number' DATA_TYPE FROM DUAL UNION ALL SELECT CA.ID ATTRIBUTE_ID , CA.COLUMN_NAME ATTRIBUTE_CODE , CASE WHEN CA.COLUMN_NAME = 'code' THEN 'Code' ELSE CAN.NAME END ATTRIBUTE_NAME , CASE CA.DATA_TYPE WHEN 'string' THEN 'String' WHEN 'number' THEN 'Number' END DATA_TYPE FROM ODF_OBJECTS O JOIN ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES CA ON O.CODE = CA.OBJECT_NAME JOIN CMN_CAPTIONS_NLS CAN ON CA.ID = CAN.PK_ID AND CAN.TABLE_NAME = 'ODF_CUSTOM_ATTRIBUTES' AND CAN.LANGUAGE_CODE = 'en' WHERE 1=1 AND ( (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ = O.CODE) OR (@WHERE:PARAM:USER_DEF:STRING:OBJECT_CODE@ IS NULL) ) AND CA.DATA_TYPE IN ('string', 'number') AND CA.EXTENDED_TYPE IS NULL) A WHERE 1=1 AND @FILTER@
